news.title: Plumbing supplier Geberit to hike prices again as costs rise
news.para: The company - seen as a proxy for the broader construction sector, as its products, such as bathroom ceramics and pipes, are so widely used - had already imposed one extraordinary price hike in January and an annual price rise in April.

news.title: Delhi HC orders Indiabulls housing to reconcile project loan accounts of Supertech
news.para: Realty developer has alleged that they have paid extra amount to Indiabulls and want to financial institution to return the amount and clear the project so that homebuyers can get the flat registered.

news.title: Delhi civic bodies planning to demolish over 2,600 unauthorised colonies: Manish Sisodia
news.para: In the last 17 years, BJP leaders in the civic bodies, councillors and mayors, and engineers "amassed money" by allowing illegal construction to flourish only to serve them notices now, Sisodia alleged.
